{"tid":1666760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尖沙咀22歲男子捱斬　警緝3刀手追查動機","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T06:50:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c80bb60edfa279cfd1e7497afb3f64c5666de9b","tid":1666760,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀柯士甸道112號近山林道交界，今晨(21日)7時14分，一名姓梁(22歲)男子途經上址時，突然被3名身穿黑色上衣男子持刀襲擊，斬傷頭及手腳。兇徒行兇後登上一輛私家車逃去。梁男血流披面，由途人協助報警。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報趕至，為男子初步包紮後將其送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。警方到場拉起封鎖線，現場留下一堆敷料及一攤血漬。經初步調查後，警方將案列作傷人，交由油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進，追緝兇徒歸案，暫未知其行兇動機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1butoa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1butoa.jpg&h=1bf0d6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191021/bkn-20191021073536823-1021_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191021%2Fbkn-20191021073536823-1021_00822_001.html&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=a043be76\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191021/bkn-20191021073536823-1021_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fa8da4fe2f90e9091621ac16230b410624743fb9","tid":1666760,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:21:49.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c5dc33e6813cec00d4b9dbe17d89b7ad846b3e","tid":1666760,"uid":225522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"黑社會糾紛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bcb544905a2c451438a9bfaaa827104e8a7d5e","tid":1666760,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:50:56.000Z","msg":"爭女！鑑定完畢！！